items.headline: Welcome to the Sonny Wiki
items.desc: Sonny is a role-playing adventure game created in flash by Krin and published through Armor Games. The main feature that sets it apart from other RPGs is that the main character, Sonny, is a zombie, and it is this key fact that the plot is structured around. It is set in a universe with a wide variation of technology; some characters use melee weapons such as clubs and swords while others use magic or guns.    The wiki serves as a collaborative encyclopedia for all aspects of Sonny and its sequels.
